verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> <S%H8761><s%> ye the YY <S%H3050><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%> <S%H8761><s%>, O ye servants <S%H5650><s%> of the YY <S%H3068><s%>, praise <S%H1984><s%> <S%H8761><s%> the name <S%H8034><s%> of the YY <S%H3068><s%>.
Blessed <S%H1288><s%> <S%H8794><s%> be the name <S%H8034><s%> of the YY <S%H3068><s%> from this time forth <S%H6258><s%> and for <S%H5704><s%> evermore <S%H5769><s%>.
From the rising <S%H4217><s%> of the sun <S%H8121><s%> unto the going down <S%H3996><s%> of the same the YY'S <S%H3068><s%> name <S%H8034><s%> is to be praised <S%H1984><s%> <S%H8794><s%>.
The YY <S%H3068><s%> is high <S%H7311><s%> <S%H8802><s%> above all nations <S%H1471><s%>, and his glory <S%H3519><s%> above the heavens <S%H8064><s%>.
Who is like unto the YY <S%H3068><s%> our 'Elohim <S%H430><s%>, who dwelleth <S%H3427><s%> <S%H8800><s%> on high <S%H1361><s%> <S%H8688><s%>,
Who humbleth <S%H8213><s%> <S%H8688><s%> himself to behold <S%H7200><s%> <S%H8800><s%> the things that are in heaven <S%H8064><s%>, and in the earth <S%H776><s%> !
He raiseht up <S%H6965><s%> <S%H8688><s%> the poor <S%H1800><s%> out of the dust <S%H6083><s%>, and lifteth <S%H7311><s%> <S%H8686><s%> the needy <S%H34><s%> out of the dunghill <S%H830><s%>;
That he may set <S%H3427><s%> <S%H8687><s%> him with princes <S%H5081><s%>, even with the princes <S%H5081><s%> of his people <S%H5971><s%>.

He maketh the barren woman <S%H6135><s%> to keep <S%H3427><s%> <S%H8688><s%> house <S%H1004><s%>, and to be a joyful <S%H8056><s%> mother <S%H517><s%> of children <S%H1121><s%>. Praise <S%H1984><s%> <S%H8761><s%> ye the YY <S%H3050><s%>.
